  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The current proposal is not in accordance with the design principles set out in the Islington Urban Design Guide, which contains a strong presumption against any extension projecting beyond the existing roofline on terraces that otherwise have an unbroken roofline, & confirms that even the existence of an isolated roof extension of a similar type elsewhere in the terrace would not normally result in this presumption being varied. The creation of the roof storey would conflict with Policies D1 (Overall design), D4 (Designing in context) & D11 (Alterations & extensions) as amplified in the Urban Design Guidelines."
